17cbdb930414671f21535378c851d88629b31a93.query:
SELECT t.world_time, t.payload
        FROM world_output t
        ORDER BY t.created DESC
        LIMIT 1

57bc09d1c766196d9a2732038610b57b5589e92e.query:
INSERT INTO user_account
            (auth0_id, display_name, email, email_verified)
        VALUES
            ($1, $2, $3, $4)
        ON CONFLICT ON CONSTRAINT email_is_unique
        DO UPDATE
        SET 
            display_name=$2,
            email_verified=$4

        FROM user_account AS ua

9fc2e8ae40472a269251380ecbadccafe435f89b.query:

    FROM scripting_schema
    ORDER BY id DESC
    LIMIT 1

c3a2fee3094e3d16733a7daa5ce4b7d0b55ee165.query:
INSERT INTO user_script (program, name, owner_id)
VALUES ($1 , $2 , (SELECT id AS owner_id FROM user_account WHERE auth0_id=$3 LIMIT 1)) ON conflict ON CONSTRAINT name_owner_id_unique DO
UPDATE
SET program=$1 RETURNING id,
                         owner_id

caecbf226cd311f3cff7d6f250e1ffe9f37bed6a.query:
SELECT user_script.name ,
       user_script.id AS script_id
FROM user_script
INNER JOIN user_account ON user_script.owner_id=user_account.id
WHERE user_account.auth0_id=$1

f132607cd466fb8564aab109e506260a47cdd7ce.query:
SELECT user_script.owner_id AS user_id ,
       user_script.name ,
       user_script.id AS script_id ,
       user_script.program AS payload
FROM user_script
INNER JOIN user_account ON user_script.owner_id=user_account.id
WHERE user_account.auth0_id=$1
    AND user_script.id=$2
